deployment.author: Christopher Atwell
deployment.message:
Add analytics and webhook modules, extend Swagger spec
Introduces Analytics and Webhook controllers, models, repositories, services, and routes. Expands Swagger OpenAPI specification with new schemas for User, Playlist, Schedule, Analytics, Webhook, and related entities, and adds /api-docs.json endpoint for OpenAPI JSON. Updates content schema and tags in Swagger, and registers new modules in the app and route index.
